                  *********** MongoDB ************

       SQL                 NoSQL

        MySQL               MongoDB                MERN
 Database               Database             Dynamic Schema / Schema less
 Table                  Collection           Faster data access
 Rows / Records         Documents            Document baud storage (JSON)
 Structured             Non Structured       Replication & HA
 Column                 Fields (JSON)        Sharding data & High Performance

        ************ Types of NoSQL Databases ************
   -  Key-value stores
   -  Column-oriented databases
   -  Document databases
   -  Graph databases
   -  Multi-Model Databases

            ********** Examples of NoSql **********
* MongoDB
* CouchDB
* Cassandra
* Amazon Dynamo DB
* RavenDB

